use the word fool resistant.

00:10:30.754 --> 00:10:32.170
There's a lot of
engineers in here

00:10:32.170 --> 00:10:34.540
and I'm sure that you
know-- every time you

00:10:34.540 --> 00:10:38.160
make something foolproof then
a bigger fool comes around.

