00:15:31.190 --> 00:15:33.240
And the real trick to
making a mayonnaise

00:15:33.240 --> 00:15:37.240
is that you have to add the
oil really, really slowly.

00:15:37.240 --> 00:15:40.990
Oh, actually-- someone
