actually relatively OK

00:26:08.410 --> 00:26:09.610
to put olive oil in there.

00:26:09.610 --> 00:26:13.782
And it's because all
that solid matter really

00:26:13.782 --> 00:26:15.240
protects the olive
oil from getting

00:26:15.240 --> 00:26:16.722
sheared by the blades spinning.

00:26:16.722 --> 00:26:19.180
So you don't notice the effect
nearly as much when you have

00:26:19.180 --> 00:26:20.640
a lot of solid matter in there.

00:26:25.800 --> 00:26:27.808
