00:43:49.794 --> 00:43:52.210
JENNA TAYLOR: How do you go
about adding vinegar to your--

00:43:52.210 --> 00:43:52.670
J. KENJI LOPEZ-ALT:
How do you feel

00:43:52.670 --> 00:43:54.650
